PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Glasses
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How do I choose the right frame for my face shape?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Choosing the right frame depends on your face shape. For round faces, try angular frames. For square faces, opt for round or oval frames. Heart-shaped faces look great with bottom-heavy frames, while oval faces suit most styles. Visit our frame guide for more detailed advice.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, we offer a wide range of prescription lenses, including single vision, bifocal, and progressive options. Simply upload your prescription during checkout or have your eye doctor send it to us directly.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What's your return policy for glasses?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We offer a 30-day return policy for all frames. If you're not satisfied with your purchase, you can return or exchange your glasses within 30 days of delivery. For prescription lenses, we offer a 90-day adaptation period.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How long does it take to receive my order?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Processing time for non-prescription glasses is typically 1-2 business days. For prescription glasses, it can take 7-10 business days. Shipping times vary depending on your location, but most orders arrive within 5-7 business days after processing.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our eyewear
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How do I know which frame size is right for me?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: We offer a virtual try-on feature and provide detailed sizing information for each frame. You can also consult our size guide or contact our customer service for personalized assistance.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes, we offer a wide range of prescription lenses including single vision, bifocal, and progressive options. Simply upload your prescription during the checkout process.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We offer a 30-day return policy for all frames and lenses. If you're not satisfied with your purchase, you can return or exchange your glasses within this period, no questions asked.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How long does it take to receive my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Processing typically takes 7-10 business days for prescription glasses. Once shipped, delivery usually takes 3-5 business days. We also offer expedited shipping options at checkout.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Do you offer any warranty on your glasses?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, all our frames come with a one-year warranty against manufacturer defects. We also offer lens coatings with extended warranties for added protection.
